    Enclosing class:
    GoogleIdToken

    @Beta
public static class GoogleIdToken.Payload
extends IdToken.Payload
    Beta
    Google ID token payload.

    Upgrade warning: in prior version 1.15 IdToken.Payload.getAccessTokenHash() and setAccessTokenHash(String) accessed "token_hash", but starting with version 1.16 they now access "at_hash".
